<i>noun</i>: 하계 [하ː계/하ː게] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>하계 [하ː계/하ː게]</dt><br>
<dd>1. mundane world; earthly world; this world</dd><br>
<dd>천상계에 상대하여, 사람이 사는 세상.</dd><br>
<dd>A world resided in by man, in contrast to some heavenly world.</dd><br>
<dd>2. lowland; low-lying area</dd><br>
<dd>높은 곳에서 낮은 곳을 이르는 말.</dd><br>
<dd>A word used to refer to a low area, in contrast with a higher place.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>